snippet.title: Star Revenge 1.5 - ST Redone V2.2 Release [Download]
snippet.description:
Well it's done! The new version of SR Redone / SR1.5. It has 125 stars which are 15 more than the old version had and half of the levels are compleatly new while others are updated older models to look better fitting to the newer times (with 3D Trees and better textures).

2.1 now has compared to 2.0 course 1, 6 and 10 changed while also putting the total star count from 121 to 125.

v2.2: https://drive.google.com/file/d/15UHaieH-czXp4uf8B7-xKnXTJWhKuVr5/view

Music in this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iKVA5OIMkgI
